WEBVTT

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:34.120
The competition is fierce
for the jobs that are available.

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:37.896
So, imagine being a young person today,

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:41.136
needing a job, seeking a livelihood,

00:03:41.160 --> 00:03:43.216
ready to build a future,

00:03:43.240 --> 00:03:46.000
and opportunities are hard to find.

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:50.096
Young people are also telling me

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:53.856
that they're worried that they're not
getting the skills that they need.

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:55.680
And again, they're right.

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:02.216
We are finding ourselves
at a time in the world